
This file contains a list of all rooms in the domain Gondor in which
you can spend or handle money.
====================================================================

Normal shops (some do not buy armours and weapons):
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/mtshop.c
Minas Morgul		- /d/Gondor/morgul/city/rooms/shop.c
Edoras			- /d/Gondor/rohan/edoras/shop.c
Rockfriends Guild	- /d/Gondor/common/dwarf_guild/shop.c
Rangers of Gondor	- /d/Gondor/common/guild/gondor/shop.c
Rangers of the North	- /d/Gondor/common/guild/north/shop.c
Rangers of Ithilien	- /d/Gondor/common/guild/north/shop.c


Armouries (buying only weapons and armours):
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/mtarms.c
Minas Morgul		- /d/Gondor/morgul/city/rooms/armoury.c
Edoras			- /d/Gondor/rohan/edoras/armoury.c
Pelargir		- /d/Gondor/pelargir/misc/pelarms.c
Dunedain		- /d/Gondor/common/dunedain/rooms/dun_shop.c
				sells also backpacks and horns.


Pubs (drinks):
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/wtpub.c
Minas Morgul		- /d/Gondor/morgul/city/rooms/pub.c
Edoras			- /d/Gondor/rohan/edoras/pspub.c
Dwarven Race Guild	- /d/Gondor/common/dwarf_guild/pub.c


Taverns (drinks and food):
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/mttavern.c
Pelargir		- /d/Gondor/pelargir/misc/sailor_pub.c
Rangers	of Gondor	- /d/Gondor/common/guild/gondor/rangerinn.c
Rangers of the North	- /d/Gondor/common/guild/north/inn.c
Rangers of Ithilien	- /d/Gondor/common/guild/ithilien/foodchamber.c


Inns (drinks, food, temporary starts):
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/old_guesthouse.c
			  and /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/innroom.c
Minas Morgul		- /d/Gondor/morgul/city/rooms/inn.c
			  and /d/Gondor/morgul/city/rooms/hotel.c
Edoras			- /d/Gondor/rohan/edoras/stallion.c
			  and /d/Gondor/rohan/edoras/hotelr.c


Bakery (light food):
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/mtbakery.c


Banks (all with gnome deposits):

For now, I think only the major cities should have access to the gem support.
After all, those are the most frequented cities and only natural the gnomes 
only put up safe guarding in such places.

Minas Tirith        - /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/mtbank.c (no real bank, just an anteroom for mtbank2)
                  and /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/mtbank2.c,    ID: #1803
Minas Morgul        - /d/Gondor/morgul/city/rooms/bank.c, ID: #1801
Pelargir            - /d/Gondor/pelargir/misc/pelbank.c,  ID: #1802
Edoras              - /d/Gondor/rohan/edoras/edbank.c


Armourers (sells and repairs armour):
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/armoury.c


Weapon Smiths:
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/wsmithy.c
			  sells weapons, sharpens and waxes weapons.
Dwarven Race Guild	- /d/Gondor/common/dwarf_guild/smith.c
			  sells axes, sharpens and waxes weapons.


Herb shops:
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/herb_shop.c
Minas Morgul		- /d/Gondor/morgul/cellar/herb_shop.c
Ranger guild		- /d/Gondor/common/guild/npc/herbalist.c


Potion shops:
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/potion_shop.c
Minas Morgul		- /d/Gondor/morgul/cellar/potion_shop.c


Jewel shops:
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/jewel_shop.c


Post offices (pigeons):
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/mtpost.c
Minas Morgul		- /d/Gondor/morgul/city/rooms/post.c
Pelargir		- /d/Gondor/pelargir/misc/pelpost.c
Edoras			- /d/Gondor/rohan/edoras/p_office.c
Rockfriends Guild	- /d/Gondor/common/dwarf_guild/post.c
Rangers	of Gondor	- /d/Gondor/common/guild/gondor/post.c
Rangers of the North	- /d/Gondor/common/guild/north/post.c
Rangers of Ithilien	- /d/Gondor/common/guild/ithilien/post.c
Morgul Mages		- /d/Gondor/common/guild2/post.c
Dunedain		- /d/Gondor/common/dunedain/post.c


Transport:
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/obj/mtwagon.c
			  Sell tickets for a carriage trip to Edoras.
Edoras			- /d/Gondor/rohan/edoras/obj/wagon.c
			  Sell tickets for a carriage trip to Minas Tirith.


Various:
Minas Tirith		- /d/Gondor/minas/rooms/stonemason.c
Pelargir		- /d/Gondor/pelargir/misc/pelstone.c
			  Both sell statues.



